<p><strong>Political posts</strong></p>
<p>2008-2009 State Secretary in the Ministry of Transport and Communications</p>
<p>2007-2008 State Secretary in the Ministry of Petroleum and Energy<br />&nbsp;<br />2005-2007 State Secretary in the Ministry of Local Government and Regional Development </p>
<p>1999-2002 Member of the Board of Centre Youth’s Central Committee <br />&nbsp;<br />1999-2000 Political advisor to the Ministry of Local Government and Regional Development </p>
<p>1995-1999 Municipal Council Representative in Steinkjer</p>
<p><strong>Work experience</strong><br />&nbsp;<br />2001-2005 Media Advisor to the Centre Party Parliamentary Group <br />&nbsp;<br />2000-2001 Internet Editor and researcher in NRK’s news department (Redaksjon 21)<br />&nbsp;<br />2000&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Arranger and press spokesman for the arrangement “Summer Camp at Stortinget”<br />&nbsp;<br />1996-1999 Working Chairman of Norges Bygdeungdomslag - The Rural Youth Association of Norway -</p>
<p><strong>Education</strong><br />&nbsp;<br />1996-2000 Ex.phil, ex.fac and basic study political science at NTNU/the University of Oslo<br />&nbsp;<br />1993-1995 Steinkjer College of Further Education, general studies</p>
<p><strong>Other posts <br /></strong>&nbsp;<br />2001-2002 Member of the Board in the Tenants’ Association<br />&nbsp;<br />1998-2001 Member of the Working Committee for Group 2050 in Verdikommisjonen - The Values Commission<br />&nbsp;<br />1996-1999 Member of the Board of Norges Bondelag (The Norwegian Farmers Association)<br />1994-1999 Vice Chairman Rural policies (94-96) and Chairman of Norges Bygdeungdomslag&nbsp; - The Rural Youth Association of Norway - (96-99)<br />&nbsp;<br />1996 and 1999 Participated in development work in villages in Guatemala for two periods<br />&nbsp;<br />1986-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Diverse local posts on Board of 4H, local and county posts with Centre Youth, posts at county level with Norges Gymnasiastsamband local and county posts with Norges Bygdeungdomslag, member of the Students’ Committee and School Committee and posts at county level and central level in Ungdom mot EU (Youth movement No to EU)<br /></p></div>
